column3: Congrats Dato Azizul. Thank you for your recent silver olympic medal.  you made us proud !!
I'm proud to tell the world that the World Champion is a Malaysian and don't underestimate my bro, ever!!!
Pocket rocket man. You deserved the champion🇲🇾💪🏼💪🏼💪🏼
What a machine. fair one Rapha
Congratulations Mr Awang.. well deserved victory!
